{"tid":192140,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"蔣麗芸建議全港辦滅鼠大賽及放置流浪貓到後巷","createTime":"2017-04-08T11:19:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-08T14:48:25.000Z","uid":53379,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b1a4167669282a43e37c24aba98e2a7b4e5131e0","tid":192140,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T11:19:20.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">蔣麗芸建議全港辦滅鼠大賽及放置流浪貓到後巷<br />\n</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n民建聯蔣麗芸在立法會財委會特別會議上表示，針對鼠患問題，估計全港有8000萬隻老鼠，雖然政府有地區清潔工作，但擔心「遠水不能救近火」，建議在全港18區舉辦滅鼠大賽，又說可以將地區的流浪貓隻放到後巷，幫助捕捉老鼠，改善鼠患。<br />\n<br />\n食物及衞生局局長高永文說，現時後巷廚餘堆積問題嚴重，認為如果有關問題得到改善，鼠患也可以受控，又說政府會增派小隊到各區做防患工作，但認為更重要是預防工作，包括公共教育和加強執法。<br />\n<br />\n高永文又說，政府有試驗計劃，去年在幾個衞生黑點安裝網絡攝錄機，又說初步成效頗好，對於有議員建議由流浪貓協助捕捉老鼠，他認為需要再驗證。<br />\n<br />\n食環署署長劉利群表示，政府會在本年5月、6月檢討有關試驗計劃，總結成效好的話，會擴展至其他地區。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1323737-20170406.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1323737-20170406.htm&d=2sQmvy6tOK2oFHH%2BrBh9lcVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=b42a7db5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1323737-20170406.htm&h=5c10a5e6\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1323737-20170406.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"294b9ce94230fbb9cc5e4e2c13443eaaee60920c","tid":192140,"uid":85586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T11:21:27.000Z","msg":"9up又有錢收<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b0623d398c0873982d52b509f906babcc2ba839","tid":192140,"uid":71216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T11:23:36.000Z","msg":"兩隻字講曬：無腦"},{"pid":"65012ca2ba7db61df8f41e92ae9beba473447187","tid":192140,"uid":17306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T11:28:23.000Z","msg":"on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d7ee2a4905739df8e953a71bfda914cccb87169","tid":192140,"uid":13504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T11:36:03.000Z","msg":"拎去DSE 小組討論做論點都嫌ON9 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f60527fdcfbb042701b2f3e0f429ed2030fa583b","tid":192140,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T11:43:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a432d64a364521a15dab2d1f74e8ef125e5a3ddc","tid":192140,"uid":34160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T11:53:15.000Z","msg":"蔣麗芸vs愛協"},{"pid":"ae955fbcc2d5af7d3042251436f353c94d1a33ef","tid":192140,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T13:31:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2420e270c2133c1485854640a81e617276bc812","tid":192140,"uid":48531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T13:34:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>蔣麗芸vs愛協</blockquote><br />\nvs貓義工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e801f4571f6a5ec751742499f54b8d820ac9040","tid":192140,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T14:48:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}